{"tid":771332,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［少甜］年少時 我與人妻有段情","createTime":"2018-08-08T01:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T12:19:05.000Z","uid":1245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5923432b9999a3eb0a8a314719ed55f5683da2","tid":771332,"uid":1245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"大家好 呢個故事是本身係舊登個既故事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係當時擺左係感情台 所以我諗知道呢個故事既巴打唔多 <br />\n所以想重新轉載比大家睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只會作少量修改同加入少甜 希望大家鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原作者寫出黎用意係回憶 話比自己知年輕時激情過 到時老左可以好好回味一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我亦問準原作者同意之下 先出呢篇文章 希望大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n首先出住一兩篇先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7a40a15138c9a49e71f7525003b2c782c55de4","tid":771332,"uid":1245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8677608bcdcfd919fe9ab714ce4be6f8671c25b2","tid":771332,"uid":1245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c32df30cf9370c053b6c390c7e2d7674bf318b","tid":771332,"uid":1245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769eb6d5ad7296d0fa3